- Dark Mode Variants

## Design Principles

### DO
- Use soft, rounded corners (never sharp)
- Create smooth transitions between states
- Use whitespace generously
- Keep animations subtle and purposeful
- Maintain consistent spacing rhythm

### DON'T
- Use harsh transitions or jarring animations
- Overcrowd layouts with dividers
- Use loud celebration effects (confetti, streaks)
- Create visual urgency patterns
- Use sharp corners on interactive elements

